						               													<description>A Most Dangerous Rescue is a race between you and the Yovuz Ustalar Gang as you attempt to rescue precious artifacts before the Yovuz Ustalar can use them for nefarious purposes. As you race across the globe searching for each artifact, you fight against members of the Yovuz Ustalar. Your travels take you to the ends of the earth and to the Boss of the Yovuz Ustalar. The world won&amp;rsquo;t be safe until you defeat the Boss or ensure that all the artifacts are out of the Yovuz Ustalar&amp;rsquo;s reach.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This is a solitaire card chase game, in which you will go from site to site to fight the 4 evil gang members one by one, trying to defeat them before they gain 4 powerful artifacts. Each gang member has its own strategy, so you should plan your game accordingly to their appearance order.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game evolves around &amp;quot;scenes&amp;quot;, when each turn is represented by a unique scene card. Each scene offers 4 different strategies to pick from. Strategies includes actions like &amp;quot;attack and research&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;attack and invest&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;research and fortify&amp;quot; etc. The evil gang member always choose his strategy first, according to his own preference and his resources, and then the player gets to retaliate.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The player needs to destroy all gang members, one by one, before time runs out. The player loses if he fails to defeat the boss before running out of time.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Occasionally, a powerful artifact will be found in a scene and the players should secure it before the Evil Yovuz Ustalar will be able to collect it.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Part of the  2022 pnp solitaire contest.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
